Package: gemini-sentry
Version: 1.0.2
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-tk, bluez, iw, libnotify-bin, pulseaudio-utils, alsa-utils
Maintainer: Jonathan & Gemini <jonathan.ray.rosenbum05@gmail.com>
Description: Continuous Proximity Monitoring Daemon
 This service monitors Bluetooth and Wi-Fi signals for approaching devices.
 Upon detection of a rapid approach, it triggers an aggressive audio/visual alarm.
 Configurable via /etc/gemini-sentry/config.json.
